<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">«سورة المرسلات»</span> <span class="c2">(٧٧)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قوله <span class="c2">«الْمُرْسَلاتِ»</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> هى الملائكة والريح..<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">«عُرْفاً»</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> يتبع بعضه بعضا يقال: جاءونى عرفا..<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">«فَالْعاصِفاتِ عَصْفاً»</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> الريح..<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">«أَلَمْ نَجْعَلِ الْأَرْضَ كِفاتاً»</span> <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> أي واعية،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span> هذا النحى كفت، وهذا كفيت.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>قال <span class="c2">«أَحْياءً وَأَمْواتاً»</span> <span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> منه ما ينبت ومنه ما لا ينبت..<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">«ماءً فُراتاً»</span> <span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> عذبا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">«جمالات صفر»</span> <span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> سود، جمل أصفر أسود..<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">«وَلا يُؤْذَنُ لَهُمْ فَيَعْتَذِرُونَ»</span> <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> مرفوعة.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>